messages.message: I think I saw a doc by @Jesika Haria (she's out on vacation but maybe @dlluncor has a reference?) with detailed IBOCR documentation. I believe it was for solutions training.. but perhaps it could be converted to customer-facing?

@Aaron Vontell we are trying to restrict the number of fields that we expose to the consumers of IBOCR.  Here is the document that we were trying to write: https://docs.google.com/document/d/1J1Y23uwHu3LGAXmQWhhS3gDnpeUBwn38a1cTWaKuqW4/edit
